text: Gandurino () is a rural locality (a selo) in Obrastsovo-Travinsky Selsoviet, Kamyzyaksky District, Astrakhan Oblast, Russia. The population was 374 as of 2010. There are 5 streets. == Geography == It is located 26 km SSW from Kamyzyak. == References == Category:Rural localities in Kamyzyaksky District
title: Gandurino
